* Sky Walk
* Pier and Waiting Room
* Ocean Front Platform

==Transportation==
The cultural park is accessible by bus from [[Siaogang Station]] of [[Kaohsiung MRT]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hougmaogang.khcc.gov.tw/eng/home02.aspx?ID=$6000&IDK=2&EXEC=D&DATA=1078 |title=Hongmaogang Cultural Park-Traffic Information |publisher=Hougmaogang.khcc.gov.tw |date=2014-01-27 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426201721/http://hougmaogang.khcc.gov.tw/eng/home02.aspx?ID=%246000&IDK=2&EXEC=D&DATA=1078 |archivedate=2014-04-26 |df= }}</ref>

